Package: BinaryEncoding
Type: Package
Title: Binary Encoding - This package converts factor or character type columns to binary columns to reduce data-size
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Anchal Khare
Maintainer: <anchalkhare.kjs@gmail.com>
Description: This takes input of dataframe having factor or character columns and converts these columns into columns having binary values for each class of factor or character column. Input data format pre-requisites - 1) Remove target variable from dataset 2)Impute missing values before using function        
Imports: 
        dplyr,
        binaryLogic
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
